    {
      "name": "tutorial_1",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Greetings, friend!",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Hi I'm here for my first day.",
          "mood": "happy"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "You must be the new recruit for the [color(purple)]Summoning Support[/color] team!",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "I'll be your mentor, nice to meet you!",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "First, we'll need to go over basic [color(purple)]Summoning[/color].",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Meet me in the next room and we'll talk more.",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "tutorial_item_none",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Here's the basics of [color(purple)]Summoning[/color]...",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "You arrange items into patterns to maximize [color(purple)]Summoning Power[/color].",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "[color(purple)]Summoning Power[/color] is your total [color(purple)]Aura[/color] times the total [color(orange)]Cross[/color].",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Each item gives either [color(purple)]Aura[/color] or [color(orange)]Cross[/color].",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "[color(green)]Bring me an item[/color] and I'll tell you about it.",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "You can also bring the item to the [color(blue)]Spellbook[/color] to learn about it.",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "I'm happy to repeat any of that, just talk to me again!",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "tutorial_3",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "See those white dots when you're holding the item?",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "If an item is on one of those dots, that means this item is [color(blue)]connected[/color] to it.",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Most items need to be connected to the circle in the center of the room. That's called the [color(red)]Nexus[/color].",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "You can look up how an item works by bringing to [color(blue)]the Spellbook[/color] at any time.",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Try [color(green)]arranging these items[/color]! I think you can get at least [color(purple)]210 Summoning Power[/color].",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "When you're ready to initiate the [color(purple)]Summoning[/color]. Interact with the [color(red)]Nexus[/color].",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "tutorial_item_candle",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "That's a Candle.",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "They gain [color(orange)]1 Cross[/color] if they're adjacent to the [color(red)]Nexus[/color].",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "We have lots of them! You can grab as many as you want from that shelf over there.",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "You can review this in the [color(blue)]Spellbook[/color].",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "tutorial_item_crystal_pawn",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Ahhh, my favorite! \nThe Crystal Pawn!",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "It impersonates [color(red)]The Nexus[/color] if it's connected to it.",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "It also chains, so a Crystal Pawn can connect to another Crystal Pawn.",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "tutorial_item_skull_candle",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "That's a Skull Candle.",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "See those white dots around you?",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "You want one of those dots to be touching [color(red)]the Nexus[/color].",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "But you also want to keep avoid anything else from being right next to it.",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Sometimes the tradeoff is worth it though. Think it through!",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "By the way, whenever you see the word \"adjacent,\" diagonals don't count.",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "tutorial_fail",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Normally you'd warp back to HQ after that.",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "If you don't meet the objective, it's OK.",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "You just won't get paid.",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "But in this case I really want to make sure you understand this stuff.",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Please try again. \nThe goal is [color(purple)]210 Summoning Power[/color] or higher!",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "shop_0",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "shopkeeper",
          "text": "Greetings.",
          "mood": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "shopkeeper",
          "text": "I am the Keeper of the Shop.",
          "mood": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "shopkeeper",
          "text": "Every time you return from a mission I'll have rotated in a new supply.",
          "mood": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "shopkeeper",
          "text": "If you're strapped for cash, take as many complimentary candles as you want.",
          "mood": "happy"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "shopkeeper",
          "text": "You'll want to load up the [color(green)]loading area on the right[/color] with as much stuff as possible.",
          "mood": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "shopkeeper",
          "text": "The area on the left is your [color(blue)]personal storage[/color].",
          "mood": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "shopkeeper",
          "text": "You can put whatever items you want there. But they won't come with you on your mission.",
          "mood": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "shopkeeper",
          "text": "Activate the loading area teleporter when you're ready to go to your assignment.",
          "mood": "normal"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "boss_0",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Hello again!",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "It's time for your first real assignment at [color(purple)]Summoning Support[/color]!",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "You're being summoned to support someone's summon.",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Try saying that 10 times fast.",
          "mood": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Go over to the room on the right to choose your assignment.",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Harder missions will give you more money, and get you promoted faster.",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "But you might want to wait until you've gotten better supplies before you do that.",
          "mood": "blue_eyes"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Supplies?",
          "mood": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "It'll make sense in a minute when you meet The Keeper.",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "boss_1",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Welcome back, Initiate!",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "boss_2",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Welcome back, Adept!",
          "mood": "green_eyes"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "alien_girl",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Hi! You can summon me something fun right?",
          "mood": "cyclops"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Fun? You paid for this ancient ritual for fun?",
          "mood": "shocked"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Yup!",
          "mood": "cyclops"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Alright then! Let's summon something fun!",
          "mood": "happy"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "armor",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "...",
          "mood": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "...",
          "mood": "armor"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Uhh... did you put in the\nsummoning request?",
          "mood": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Yes. My old wearer was tragically murdered after doffing me.",
          "mood": "armor"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Oh.",
          "mood": "worried"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "You can summon something that will be able to wear me right?",
          "mood": "armor"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "I.. think so? I'll try my best!",
          "mood": "shocked"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Wonderful! Hopefully they will last longer than my last wearer.",
          "mood": "armor"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "zombie",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Brains. It's gotta have lots of brains.",
          "mood": "zombie"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Oh. Right.",
          "mood": "shocked"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Last summon I ordered had \nalmost no brains.",
          "mood": "zombie"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Oh, I'm sure that was... disappointing?",
          "mood": "worried"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Very! It's so hard to get someone to play Rummy with me these days.",
          "mood": "zombie"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "green_guy",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "First day?",
          "mood": "green_coworker"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Yup!",
          "mood": "shocked"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Don't forget, carpet nullifies ritual items.\nNot sure why, lot's of theories out there.\nI just know it sucks cleaning wax out of it.",
          "mood": "green_coworker"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "purple_guy",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Hey, let me enjoy my break.\nCheck back later when I'm working.",
          "mood": "purple_coworker"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "pink_guy",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "You have an appointment?",
          "mood": "pink_coworker"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Nope?",
          "mood": "worried"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "coworker",
          "text": "Come back when you have an appointment.\nThe Summon Incorpeal Board members have a busy schedule.",
          "mood": "pink_coworker"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "yellow_dress",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Hey. Got anything spicy?",
          "mood": "cyan_hair"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Spicy? Uhh... like hot?",
          "mood": "shocked"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Nah. Spicy. You know.",
          "mood": "cyan_hair"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "...Right. Anything specific?",
          "mood": "shocked"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Surprise me!",
          "mood": "cyan_hair"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Okay then, one giant sandworm coming up!",
          "mood": "happy"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "cowboy",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Thanks for choosing Summons Incorpeal for your summoning needs.",
          "mood": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "How can I help you today?",
          "mood": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Uh. You can summon me a horse right?",
          "mood": "cowboy_unamused"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Of course! One horse coming up!",
          "mood": "happy"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Yipee!",
          "mood": "cowboy_happy"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Make  sure it's not on fire like \nthe last one though!",
          "mood": "cowboy_angry"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "The last horse summoned for you was on fire?!",
          "mood": "shocked"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "glasses",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "I heard you guys could summon anything?",
          "mood": "glasses"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Almost anything, yup!\nWhat would you like?",
          "mood": "happy"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Oh boy! Can you summon me a dog?",
          "mood": "glasses"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Of course! Any specific breed?",
          "mood": "happy"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Yup! A golden summoner.",
          "mood": "glasses"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "You mean a retriever?",
          "mood": "normal"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Same thing!",
          "mood": "glasses"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "mother",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "You're late! Hurry up with the summon for my birthday boy!",
          "mood": "blonde_hair"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Oh. Right away!",
          "mood": "worried"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "I swear, next time I'm just ordering from the River Styx online marketplace!",
          "mood": "blonde_hair"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "son",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "Hey man. Sorry about my mom. I'm happy with whatever.",
          "mood": "moustache"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "No worries! I'll try to summon \nsomething fun!",
          "mood": "happy"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "father",
      "lines": [
        {
          "speaker_id": "customer",
          "text": "It's our boy's birthday! My favorite time of the year! Help yourself to cupcakes!",
          "mood": "notch"
        },
        {
          "speaker_id": "player",
          "text": "Oh, thanks! You know... I could make use of a few of those.",
          "mood": "happy"
        }
      ]
